
Overview of noun salve

The noun salve has 2 senses (first 2 from tagged texts)
                                          
1. (1) ointment, unction, unguent, balm, salve -- (semisolid preparation (usually containing a medicine) applied externally as a remedy or for soothing an irritation)
2. (1) salve -- (anything that remedies or heals or soothes; "he needed a salve for his conscience")

Overview of verb salve

The verb salve has 2 senses (no senses from tagged texts)
                                        
